---
title: Toasted Rice Bowls with Sweet Potatoes, Sugar Snap Peas and Cashews
description: After-dinner grazers and midnight snackers, take note of tonight's dinner! This veggie rice bowl is hearty and loaded with flavour, which means your stomach definitely won't be grumbling tonight. Plus, it's got all the Asian-fusion flavours we love: soy, ginger and garlic.
